"Aziraphale, for God- for Satan- for somebody's sake, where are you?!"

This hurts my heart

AH! How he raises his sword but then threatens never to talk to him again instead...

... and it works.
Can we all just agree that when they say “to the world” they’re really talking about each other?

— I don't even like you.
— You doooooo.

Omg, I'm crying.
